title: Princess
description: The first book in the widely acclaimed Maiden Series by Aishing MorganWhen Elethrine, Princess Talithea and their maid, Aisla, threaten to spank sorceress Ea, they are punished by being transported to a distant part of their world. This book charts their journey home through a series of erotic indignities and humiliations.
author: Aishling Morgan
